metadata.name: Rock Monster - Ice
metadata.description:
From the creative mind of The CannaMan, this epic rock monster is ready to SMASH into any metaverse! 

Crushing foes in the blink of an eye, this bad-ass creature will bring an incomparable level of entertainment to your virtual space!

This GLB file can be utilized in Spatial.io and many other blockchain integrated systems. The default comes with a tidy animation, while ownership allows you access to the base files, continued support, and multiple formats for use in Unity, Spatial, or any other 3D platform.

Whether you are a collector looking for a neat "action figure," or a developer looking for your next NPC or Boss, you will be proud to have this NFT in your wallet!
